---
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import Section from '../ui/Section.astro';
import botanicalImg from '../../assets/images/plants.png';
---

<Section id="about" title="About Bosque">
  <div class="about-content">
    <div class="about-text">
      <p class="lead">
        Nestled in the heart of San Francisco's vibrant Mission District, Bosque offers an intimate wine bar experience that celebrates the natural beauty of both wine and food.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our carefully curated selection features natural wines from small producers, paired with seasonal plates that highlight local ingredients. The name "Bosque" - meaning forest in Spanish - reflects our commitment to organic, earth-driven flavors and our cozy, woodland-inspired atmosphere.
      </p>
      <p>
        Whether you're discovering a new favorite vintage or enjoying familiar classics, our knowledgeable staff is here to guide your journey through our ever-evolving menu of wines and seasonal specialties.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-image">
      <Image
        src={botanicalImg}
        alt="Botanical illustration representing our natural approach"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </div>
</Section>

<style>
  .about-content {
    display: grid;
    gap: 3rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .about-text {
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .about-text p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-image {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .about-image img {
    max-width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .about-image {
      display: none;
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .about-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>